   324	| Baseline degradation row | Supervisor response | Trigger |
   325	|---|---|---|
   380	executing, stop it from continuing to assert steering on a **frozen or stale solution** (H4) —
   381	a frozen estimator does not advance the solution sequence, so `R` does not fire, the lease
   382	expires, and the *live* supervisor executes a Case-A revocation.
   383	
   384	Its **limits**, now stated (correcting the previous over-claim): the watchdog **cannot** act
   385	once its own process has died or the link is lost (Case B) — it is inside the failed domain.
