   389	`uncontrolled-pending-evidence` and the physical layer is the only present backstop — not the
   390	internal watchdog and not an assumed timeout action. Independence properties that do hold: the
   391	watchdog runs on the monotonic clock (a device/UTC reset or spoofed label cannot extend it),
